[h1]Raid hits. Your soldiers draft instantly.[/h1]

[b]Auto Draft[/b] detects hostile threats and instantly drafts your combat-capable colonists. Non-combatants flee to safety. When the danger passes, soldiers auto-undraft and return to work.

[b]You keep full manual control[/b] of drafted pawns. Auto Draft just handles the drafting -- you give the orders.

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Features[/h1]

[list]
[*] [b]Instant threat detection[/b] -- checks every second for hostiles
[*] [b]Skill-based soldiers[/b] -- only drafts pawns above minimum combat skill (configurable)
[*] [b]Auto-undraft[/b] -- soldiers stand down when all threats eliminated
[*] [b]Non-combatant flee[/b] -- pacifists sprint to safest roofed area
[*] [b]Player override[/b] -- manually undraft a soldier and they stay undrafted
[*] [b]Configurable delay[/b] -- wait before undrafting after last threat
[*] [b]Draft/undraft alerts[/b]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]The Combat Pipeline[/h1]

Works perfectly with other LxO mods:
[list]
[*] [b]Auto Draft[/b] -- drafts soldiers when threat appears
[*] [b]Smart Gear[/b] -- auto-equips combat gear (respects manual control while drafted)
[*] [b]Learn to Survive[/b] -- Combat Instinct improves fighting behavior
[*] [b]Smart Allow[/b] -- auto-allows dropped loot after combat
[/list]

Threat -> Draft -> Fight -> Undraft -> Re-equip -> Allow loot. All automatic.

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Settings[/h1]

[list]
[*] Min combat skill slider (default: 4)
[*] Undraft delay slider
[*] Non-combatant flee toggle
[*] Alert toggle
[/list]

[h1]Compatibility[/h1]
[list]
[*] Works with any mod
[*] Safe to add or remove mid-save
[/list]

[h1]Requirements[/h1]
[list]
[*] RimWorld 1.6+
[*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=2009463077]Harmony[/url]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Languages[/h1]
English, German, Chinese Simplified, Japanese, Korean, Russian, Spanish

